⭐ Roadmap (English Version)
v1.1 – Quality Update
Improved UI (cleaner layout, better spacing)

Added basic settings (default export path)

Fixed minor user‑reported issues

Optimized application startup

v1.2 – Export Enhancements
Support for additional export formats

Ability to choose the target folder directly in the app

Data preview before export

Logging of recent exports

v1.3 – User Experience Update
Dark / Light mode

Improved error messages

Enhanced animations and transitions

Option to minimize to system tray

v2.0 – Advanced Features
Plugin system (extendable architecture)

Scheduled automatic exports

Cloud sync for settings

Professional edition (DataSmith2 Pro)

Long‑term Ideas
Web version

Mobile companion app

Integration with other tools for artists

AI‑assisted export presets
